---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — La Belle Medical Aesthetic Clinic"
  description="Privacy Policy for La Belle Medical Aesthetic Clinic in Quispamsis, New Brunswick. Learn how we collect, use and protect your personal information."
>

  <div class="privacy-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--rose)">Legal</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="divider divider--left"></div>
      <p class="privacy-hero__meta">Last updated: January 1, {year}</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section privacy-body">
    <div class="container privacy-container">

      <p class="lead">La Belle Medical Aesthetic Clinic ("La Belle," "we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our website or use our services.</p>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We collect personal information you voluntarily provide when you:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Book an appointment through our website or JaneApp booking platform</li>
          <li>Complete a contact form or send us an email</li>
          <li>Call our clinic</li>
          <li>Subscribe to our newsletter or promotions</li>
          <li>Become a patient at our clinic</li>
        </ul>
        <p>This information may include your name, email address, phone number, date of birth, health history, and treatment records as required for medical care.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the personal information we collect to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Schedule and manage your appointments</li>
          <li>Provide medical aesthetic treatments and follow-up care</li>
          <li>Communicate with you about your appointments, treatments, and promotions</li>
          <li>Comply with legal and regulatory requirements for medical records</li>
          <li>Improve our website and services</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>3. Medical Records</h2>
        <p>As a medical aesthetic clinic, we are required to maintain accurate patient records in compliance with New Brunswick provincial health regulations. Your medical information is kept strictly confidential and is only accessible to authorized clinical staff involved in your care.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services that may collect information:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>JaneApp</strong> — our appointment booking platform, governed by their own privacy policy</li>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — for anonymous website traffic analysis</li>
          <li><strong>Social Media Platforms</strong> — Facebook and Instagram, governed by their respective privacy policies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
        <p>Our website uses cookies to enhance your browsing experience. These include essential cookies required for the website to function, and analytics cookies to help us understand how visitors use our site. You may disable cookies through your browser settings, though this may affect website functionality.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>6. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction. Our website uses SSL encryption for all data transmission.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under applicable Canadian privacy law (PIPEDA), you have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Access the personal information we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request correction of inaccurate information</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for non-medical communications at any time</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your information (subject to medical record retention requirements)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>8. Retention of Information</h2>
        <p>We retain patient records for a minimum of ten (10) years following your last visit, as required by New Brunswick health regulations. Contact and marketing information is retained until you request removal or withdraw consent.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your personal information, please contact us:</p>
        <address class="privacy-address">
          <strong>La Belle Medical Aesthetic Clinic</strong><br />
          208 Hampton Rd<br />
          Quispamsis, NB&nbsp;&nbsp;E2E 4L8<br /><br />
          Phone: <a href="tel:5068490271">506-849-0271</a><br />
          Email: <a href="mailto:Labellemedclinic@gmail.com">Labellemedclinic@gmail.com</a>
        </address>
      </div>

      <div class="privacy-section">
        <h2>10. Updates to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The "last updated" date at the top of this page reflects the most recent revision. Continued use of our website following any changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
.privacy-hero {
  background: var(--cream-dark);
  padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
  margin-top: 80px;
}
.privacy-hero__meta {
  font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--charcoal-mid);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

.privacy-container {
  max-width: 740px;
}

.privacy-body .lead {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--charcoal-mid);
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
}

.privacy-section {
  margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(213,164,148,0.2);
}
.privacy-section:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}
.privacy-section h2 {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--charcoal);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.privacy-section p,
.privacy-section li {
  font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  line-height: 1.9;
  color: var(--charcoal-mid);
}
.privacy-section ul {
  padding-left: 1.5rem;
  margin: 0.75rem 0;
}
.privacy-section li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.privacy-section a { color: var(--rose); }
.privacy-section a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

.privacy-address {
  font-style: normal;
  font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  line-height: 2;
  color: var(--charcoal-mid);
  background: var(--cream-dark);
  padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
  border-left: 3px solid var(--rose);
  margin-top: 1rem;
}
.privacy-address a { color: var(--rose); }
</style>
